metadata.name: VERNAL LOVE
metadata.description:
I was so on a birding trip to Munnar,booked a hide at Kuttetans Hide,whenever I go there I get something special,this time it was extraordinary.Vernal Hanging Parrot Couple,look how cute they are.After a tiring 3 hour wait I got this picture,I was so happy for getting such an amazing photograph.
Captured with Nikon D500 and nikon 200-500mm lens
